A plugin for GetSimple CMS to automatically resize images that have been inserted and resized in the WYSIWYG editor.


**************** Troubleshooting ****************
=Some pages don't show after I insert an image.=
Check to see how big the images are. Depending on your webhost, you may be running out of memory while resizing the images.


Written by William Johnston (http://www.manystrands.com/)
simple_html_dom.php is written by S.C. Chen (http://simplehtmldom.sourceforge.net/).